nodes.text: This  Tusken Raider was the chief of a little tribe which migrated to the other end of Tatooine because of the soil erosion. When they out of stock the elder warriors persuaded him, to go back and bring them food and other goods. Then he left his tribe, including his wife and daughter, but promised, he will come back in the next season with warriors and food. When he returned at the end of the season he found they base empty.
